          <p class="mb-1" style="font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700;">© 2025 CodeHashers. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p class="text-secondary" style="font-size: 1.6rem;">Made with ❤️ by CodeHashers Team</p>
